          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>Hou hast slain <hi rend="italics">Horace</hi>, what shou'd hinder</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-2" n="2">Thy Muse from falling upon <hi rend="italics">Pindar</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-3" n="3">But e'er you mount his mettled Steed,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-4" n="4">Beware, <hi rend="italics">O Bard</hi>, how you proceed.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-5" n="5">If you shou'd give him once the Reins,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-6" n="6">High up in Air he'll turn your Brains;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-7" n="7">And if you shou'd his Fury check,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666BD514-line-8" n="8">'Tis ten to one, he breaks your Neck.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
